This font is based on the corporate font for the game The Mandate. The Mandate is a science fiction roleplaying game which sees the player as a disgraced space captain who gets one chance at redemption and is the last desperate hope for the newly crowned Empress to restore peace and secure the future of humanity.
Find out more at www.mandategame.com
